OL,6,FThey were employed by Al Fayed's
OL,7,Fprivate airline Fayair, or by the Al
OL,8,FFayed family, and allege they were
OL,9,Fsubjected to "serious sexual abuse,
OL,10,Fharassment and mistreatment".
OL,12,FLawyer Richard Meeran, from Leigh Day,
OL,13,Fsaid: "We have taken this step on
OL,14,Fbehalf of those of our clients who
OL,15,Fwere abused by Al Fayed while working
OL,16,Ffor him or his other businesses
OL,17,Foutside of Harrods.
