OL,6,F"Much of the media reporting around Al
OL,7,FFayed's decades of depraved and
OL,8,Fpredatory behaviour has centred around
OL,9,Fhis work at Harrods but it is
OL,10,Fimportant that his estate is also made
OL,11,Flegally accountable for the widespread
OL,12,Fabuse he perpetrated against those who
OL,13,Fmay never have had dealings with the
OL,14,Ffamous store.
OL,16,F"Our clients took on roles as
OL,17,Fprofessionals and should have been
OL,18,Fable to expect a safe working
OL,19,Fenvironment, instead they were
OL,20,Fsubjected to serious sexual abuse,
OL,21,Fharassment and mistreatment.
