OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police is currently
OL,7,Freviewing a total of 21 allegations
OL,8,Fthat were made before Al Fayed died in
OL,9,F2023, and referred two of these to the
OL,10,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,11,F(IOPC) last November.
OL,13,FMore than 100 alleged victims have
OL,14,Fcontacted police to say they were
OL,15,Fsexually abused by the tycoon, the
OL,16,Fyoungest of whom is thought to have
OL,17,Fbeen 13 at the time.
OL,19,FA number of allegations were made
OL,20,Fagainst him while he was still alive.
